{"tid":762551,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔見銀包]有冇人喺小巴89B執到個綠色銀包？","createTime":"2018-07-31T11:25:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-02T03:48:42.000Z","uid":34553,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c1a68961e285bec0a1331fa1ffedfa54bc980510","tid":762551,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T11:25:21.000Z","msg":"今日1730搭89B喺石頭街落車<br />\n坐單丁尾二個位<br />\n落車發覺漏咗個綠色銀包<br />\n入面有身份證、幾張信用卡、幾百現金、相等等<br />\n打咗小巴電話但覆返搵唔到<br />\n去咗警署報埋失<br />\n有冇巴絲執到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔求現金喺度<br />\n但求身份證同卡冇唔見<br />\n薄酬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自製皮銀包深綠色<br />\n入面有個散銀格<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/31/192500_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F31%2F192500_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=d6f6519b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48b79056f67f530ace36730284d424ff4745443e","tid":762551,"uid":34553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T11:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"429aeeef6c7a9e6f124fa07483fbd3cc60da4d07","tid":762551,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T11:28:51.000Z","msg":"Good luck"},{"pid":"174981f2e414f69067e0ccf5dd4a4ba4ea14a066","tid":762551,"uid":34553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"429aeeef6c7a9e6f124fa07483fbd3cc60da4d07","tid":762551,"uid":35930,"like":0,